00:06:48.946 --> 00:06:52.936 A:middle
And it's amazing how much an

00:06:52.936 --> 00:06:54.866 A:middle
experience can change when

00:06:54.866 --> 00:06:56.756 A:middle
actions are removed from the UI.

00:06:56.756 --> 00:06:58.986 A:middle
